}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The revision of this adapter is not specified on the device. It is not known if it is on printed on a label affixed to the box, either..
"M01-URET.-A30" is silkscreened on a production unit's board (S/N: '''UR03049702'''). :"M01-URE450R REV:X10" and a '''Plotech''' logo is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
The FCC docs for the URE450T state this device was also sold by '''TRENDnet''' ('''TRENDware''') as the TU-10T.
